@startuml diff_and_changelog
title As-Is/To-Be Diff and Changelog Generation

participant "Software Architect" as architect
participant "Evolution" as bausteinsicht_cli_evolution
participant "Diff" as bausteinsicht_diff
participant "Changelog" as bausteinsicht_changelog

architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_evolution : 1. bausteinsicht diff ‑‑to-be target.jsonc
bausteinsicht_cli_evolution -> bausteinsicht_diff : 2. compare(asIsModel, toBeModel)
bausteinsicht_diff --> bausteinsicht_cli_evolution : 3. added / removed / changed elements and relationships
architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_evolution : 4. bausteinsicht changelog ‑‑since v1.0.0
bausteinsicht_cli_evolution -> bausteinsicht_changelog : 5. for each relevant git ref: load model at that ref
bausteinsicht_changelog -> bausteinsicht_diff : 6. compare(modelAtRefN, modelAtRefN+1)
bausteinsicht_diff --> bausteinsicht_changelog : 7. delta per ref
bausteinsicht_changelog --> architect : 8. chronological architecture changelog (AsciiDoc/Markdown)

@enduml
